snippet.textDisplay: I agree 100% with you concerning the size. I'd rather have a tablet that folds to pocket-sized. But this isn't going for that "more portable" factor, it's just going for 100% coolness. It's completely unique. You pull one of these out and you're probably the only person in the room that has one and everyone will probably want to see what the hell it is. That's not a knock against it at all. NGL I kinda want one. Been an iPhone guy for like 10 years now but innovations like this make me actually excited about a phone like I haven't been in years. Sure, it's a gimmick but holy crap it's a cool gimmick.
